text: Nebojša Vučinić (born 17 October 1953) is a Montenegrin judge born in Cetinje, Montenegro and was the judge of the European Court of Human Rights in respect of Montenegro until July 2018. ==References== Category:1953 births Category:Living people Category:Judges of the European Court of Human Rights Category:Montenegrin judges of international courts and tribunals Category:Montenegrin judges
title: Nebojša Vučinić
